<br>
Then it can be used in Velk, even at village. I did it a lot and never get a train.<br>
Of course, if you are at frienzy with an enchanter and he mezz some mob, using an ae does not seem a good idea if you want to be reinvited.<br>
<br>
Hate and KK are dungeons in which you can aggro upper (or lower) floor, any AE is a noway use !<br>
